title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show

description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, Fritzy wants to celebrate an anniversary with DP...only issue is that he has the wrong date. Reggie Miller calls in to preview the NBA Finals and make his prediction for who will win it all.
